oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Lester Flatt and Osborne Brothers at Nelson Junior High School (17049)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Flatt, Lester; Osborne Brothers;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and blue on white) announcing Lester Flatt and the Osborne Brothers at the Nelson Count Junior High School in Lovingston, Virginia on November 10. Poster features metal photoplates of Lester Flatt, the Osborne Brothers, and Martha White Flour. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/39148.
